Our story starts on the morning of June the 18th, 1982, in London.

00:01:09.740 --> 00:01:16.480
As you may know, the river Thames runs through the centre of London dividing north and south.

00:01:17.640 --> 00:01:23.275
A young postal clerk was on his way to work, and was walking across one of

